description: Three people who continue to test positive for Covid-19 cannot transmit it, says the health minister.
title: Coronavirus Isle of Man: 'No risk' from three who continue to test positive
title_page: Coronavirus Isle of Man: 'No risk' from three who continue to test positive - BBC News
maintext: "We know from studies around the world that a lot of people either don't present symptoms at all, or they develop such low level symptoms that they dismiss it as something else," he added.
